support ubuntu 14.04
Usage:	./zopenconfig.sh [-h]  <Service_Name> [Action] [-v]

optional arguments:
	-h,--help	show this help message and exit
	-v,--version	show the version of these bash scripts

**For example**
	./zopenconfig.sh package_test
	./zopenconfig.sh show
	./zopenconfig.sh user
	./zopenconfig.sh role
	./zopenconfig.sh tenant
